When scrolled to the bottom of the page, more results seems to be loading but it does not show up in the UI.

Checking the network tab in developer tools, you can see that Bamboo is calling the following REST api for more results: {{/rest/api/latest/deploy/project/1441793/versions?after=true&before=false&start-index=15&max-result=15}}

The missing releases from the UI can be seen in the response body of the request.

maven 3.3.1 no longer supports win9x and they dropped the mvn.bat executable, replacing it with mvn.cmd.

However com.atlassian.bamboo.plugins.maven.task.M3Config class in bamboo will explicitly use .bat. (5.8 branch sources)  I haven't tested on a real running windows agent, but I'm assuming the  3.3.1 maven cannot be run on windows agents at the time being..

{code}
    public static String getExecutableName()
    {
        return ExecutablePathUtils.makeBatchIfOnWindows(M2_EXECUTABLE_NAME);
    }
{code}

please for details see https://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MNG-5776

{{bamboo.planRepository.revision.number}} throws a substitution error.
{{bamboo.planRepository.lastchange.revision.number}} doesn't get substituted.

To reproduce:
Create a plan with SVN repo http://googletest.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ and a Script Task with the following inline commands:
{noformat}
echo ----------------
echo 1a ${bamboo.planRepository.1.revision}
echo 2a ${bamboo.planRepository.1.revision.number}
echo 3a ${bamboo.planRepository.1.lastchange.revision.number}
echo 4a ${bamboo.planRepository.1.repositoryUrl}
echo
echo 1b ${bamboo.planRepository.revision}
echo 2b ${bamboo.planRepository.revision.number}
echo 3b ${bamboo.planRepository.lastchange.revision.number}
echo 4b ${bamboo.planRepository.repositoryUrl}
echo
echo deprecated
echo 4 ${bamboo.repository.revision.number}
echo 5 ${bamboo.repository.previous.revision.number}
echo 6 ${bamboo.custom.svn.revision.number}
echo 7 ${bamboo.custom.svn.lastchange.revision.number}
echo 8 ${bamboo.repository.svn.repositoryUrl}
echo ----------------

{noformat}

